  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Game </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you strong enough to survive the <strong>Eternal Rain</strong>? Work out a strategy to beat the relentless onslaught of monsters for 15 minutes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon a friendly forest spirit, use the power of pyromancy or shoot tons of bullets to annihilate your nightmares. With the help of your characters unique powers and the smart use of all possible upgrades you will be an unstoppable hero.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > Choose Your Character </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use acquired <strong>Soul Leaves </strong>to buy new characters:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Azami, the Rogue & Charon, the Grim Reaper</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/b63104765566510f37782be25000e1da.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/a20762b82f7cf9fec2faa9fecb2900a8.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Fang, the Alchemist & Helios, the Lord of Ashes</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/4d84bfac25841a602fbb6cc81fdfcfb0.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/ff53f5d715f3080b7936dda1ce7462b8.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lilly, the Blade of Death & Stefanie, the Trigger-happy</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/63ab3ada6688e760327c8298451bc946.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/5a50bb273c8c64e23b37fed43d3365d5.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scrim, the Dragonkin & Leo, Guide of Souls</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/3cecafc3d68379cd196b39bf4226df46.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990970/extras/df734bbda1a66b50bfdcfa19cdf26b1a.avif?t=1737621446\" width=200 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features </strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Diverse Characters & Upgrades: Over 40 different upgrades and 6 playable characters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Character Ascensions: Unique Upgrades for each character</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Monsoon System: A difficulty system with currently up to 5 increasing challenges to spice up your game </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Quick Gameplay: Fast and yet precise gameplay with the ability to dash</p></li></ul>",
